%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Commission%20said%20five%20Caribbean%20nations%20%E2%80%93%20Antigua%20and%20Barbuda%2C%20Grenada%2C%20St%20Kitts%20and%20Nevis%2C%20St%20Lucia%2C%20and%20Dominica%20%E2%80%93%20have%20granted%20citizenship%20to%20at%20least%2088%2C000%20individuals%20for%20as%20little%20as%20%24100%2C000%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20cases%2C%20the%20number%20of%20passports%20issued%20is%20higher%20than%20the%20existing%20population.%20St%20Kitts%20and%20Nevis%2C%20which%20has%20a%20population%20of%2048%2C000%2C%20has%20issued%2036%2C700%20passports%20to%20foreign%20individuals%2C%20per%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20an%20investigation%20by%20news%20organizations%20including%20The%20Guardian%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.occrp.org%2Fen%2Finvestigations%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOrganized%20Crime%20and%20Corruption%20Reporting%20Project%3C%2Fa%3E%20(OCCRP)%20revealed%20that%20Dominica%20had%20sold%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcountries-buy-citizenship-golden-passport-countries-list-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bgolden%20passports%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20individuals%20including%20a%20former%20Afghan%20spy%20and%20a%20colonel%20under%20former%20Libyan%20dictator%20Muammar%20Gaddafi.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20scale%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bgolden%20passport%26quot%3B%20trade%20has%20sparked%20security%20concerns%20from%20the%20European%20Commission%2C%20which%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhome-affairs.ec.europa.eu%2Fsystem%2Ffiles%2F2023-10%2FRegulation%2520proposal%2520revision%2520of%2520the%2520visa%2520suspension%2520mechanism_en.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproposing%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20crackdown%20on%20visa-free%20travel%20for%20people%20using%20them.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20proposal%20said%20obtaining%20citizenship%20through%20investment%20schemes%20could%20lead%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Binfiltration%20of%20organised%20crime%2C%20money%20laundering%2C%20tax%20evasion%2C%20and%20corruption.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20legislation%20would%20end%20visa%20exemptions%20for%20countries%20that%20operate%20investor%20citizenship%20schemes%20for%20buyers%20who%20lack%20a%20%26quot%3Bgenuine%20link%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20150%2C000%20people%20have%20used%20the%20visa-free%20travel%20arrangements%20to%20claim%20asylum%20once%20in%20a%20European%20country%2C%20according%20to%20the%20EU%20home%20affairs%20commissioner%2C%20Ylva%20Johansson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20of%20course%20not%20how%20the%20visa-free%20travelling%20should%20be%20used%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fbusiness%2F2023%2Foct%2F19%2Fcaribbean-states-sold-golden-assports-eu-citizenship-travel%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuying%20a%20passport%20lets%20wealthy%20individuals%20circumvent%20immigration%20regulations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20system%20that%20allows%20them%20to%20%26quot%3Bskirt%20the%20rules%26quot%3B%20is%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20problematic%2C%26quot%3B%20Gary%20Kalman%2C%20the%20executive%20director%20of%20Transparency%20International%20US%2C%20previously%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20passports%20became%20more%20popular%20after%20citizens%20of%20the%20Caribbean%20countries%20were%20granted%20visa-free%20travel%20in%202015%2C%20The%20Guardian%20reported.%20However%2C%20buyers%20are%20not%20required%20to%20have%20any%20connection%20to%20the%20states%2C%20nor%20even%20visit%20the%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frich-russians-offered-caribbean-shortcut-us-visas-grenada-passport-2022-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInsider%20investigation%3C%2Fa%3E%20revealed%20a%20similar%20loophole%20that%20gave%20rich%20Russians%20a%20backdoor%20to%20the%20US%20by%20investing%20as%20litt