%2007%2C%202023%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC.%3Cp%3EChip%20Somodevilla%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20IRS%20said%20it's%20made%20more%20progress%20in%20tracking%20down%20taxes%20millionaires%20owe.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20also%20closed%20some%20cases%2C%20including%20a%20taxpayer%20deducting%20expenses%20to%20build%20a%20mega-mansion.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThere's%20more%20enforcement%20to%20come%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IRS%20says%20its%20mission%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20higher-earning%20tax%20dodgers%20has%20yielded%20%24122%20million%20more%20from%20just%20100%20millionaires%20%E2%80%94%20and%20they've%20already%20closed%20several%20cases%20of%20particularly%20brazen%20evasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20passage%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-reduction-act-how-it-reduces-price-growth-deficit-pressures-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInflation%20Reduction%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20infused%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdemocrats-big-climate-tax-bill-make-tax-refund-on-time-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebillions%20of%20dollars%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20the%20previously%20perpetually%20underfunded%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeet-irs-worker-trying-to-get-you-your-tax-refund-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epaper-laden%20IRS%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20good%20chunk%20of%20that%20was%20earmarked%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-in-the-irs-overhaul-tax-enforcement-wealthy-corporations-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eincreased%20enforcement%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%2C%20in%20a%20new%20announcement%2C%20the%20IRS%20said%20that%20enforcement%20is%20only%20ramping%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPrior%20to%20the%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act%2C%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20of%20budget%20cuts%20prevented%20the%20IRS%20from%20keeping%20pace%20with%20the%20increasingly%20complicated%20methods%20the%20wealthiest%20tax%20taxpayers%20used%20to%20hide%20their%20income%20and%20evade%20their%20paying%20their%20fair%20share%20of%20taxes%2C%26quot%3B%20IRS%20Commissioner%20Daniel%20Werfel%20told%20reporters%20in%20a%20call.%20%26quot%3BInflation%20Reduction%20Act%20funding%20gives%20us%20the%20ability%20to%20take%20swift%20and%20aggressive%20action%20to%20improve%20compliance%20and%20close%20the%20tax%20gap.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20IRA%2C%20the%20IRS%20has%20closed%20several%20cases%20of%20high-earning%20taxpayers%20getting%20creative%20with%20their%20business%20expenses%20and%20deductions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%20case%2C%20according%20to%20Werfel%2C%20a%20former%20CEO%20was%20sentenced%20to%20a%20year%20in%20prison%20and%20ordered%20to%20pay%20over%20%2415%20million%20because%20he%20was%20deducting%20personal%20expenses%20as%20business%20expenses%2C%20and%20using%20that%20to%20finance%20his%20construction%20of%20a%2051%2C000%20square%20foot%20mansion.%20Some%20of%20those%20expenses%20he%20claimed%20included%20an%20outdoor%20pool%2C%20pool%20house%2C%20and%20tennis%2C%20basketball%2C%20and%20bocce%20courts%2C%20according%20to%20Werfel%2C%20alongside%20falsifying%20millions%20for%20luxury%20vehicles%2C%20artwork%2C%20country%20club%20memberships%2C%20and%20homes%20for%20his%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20cases%20Werfel%20highlighted%3A%20A%20restaurant%20owner%20skimming%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20from%20his%20business%20to%20spend%20on%20himself%20and%20gamble%2C%20all%20while%20filing%20false%20tax%20returns.%20And%20in%20another%20case%2C%20someone%20received%20over%20%245%20million%20in%20COVID-relief%20loans%20for%20a%20sham%20business%2C%20and%20then%20used%20that%20money%20to%20buy%20Ferrari%2C%20Bentley%2C%20and%20Lamborghini%20cars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20IRS%20is%20specifically%20taking%20aim%20at%20Americans%20who%20earn%20over%20%241%20million%2C%20and%20have%20over%20%24250%2C000%20in%20tax%20debt.%20An%20IRS%20memo%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frich-people-tax-evasion-owe-billions-returns-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Epreviously%20viewed%20by%20Insider%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed%20that%20nearly%201%2C000%20taxpayers%20making%20over%20%241%20million%20annually%20did%20not%20file%20their%20taxes%20multiple%20times%20between%202015%20to%202020.%20That%20group%20of%20taxpayers%20%E2%80%94%20of%20whom%2058%20earn%20at%20least%20%2410%20million%20%E2%80%94%20were%20estimated%20by%20the%20IRS%20to%20owe%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eover%20%2434%20billion%20as%20of%20May%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20the%20IRS%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irs.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Firs-announces-sweeping-effort-to-restore-fairness-to-tax-system-with-inflation-reduction-act-funding-new-compliance-efforts%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esaid%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20was%20contacting%201%2C600%20of%20those%20millionaires%20who%20owe%20over%20%24250%2C000%20to%20try%20and%20get%20those%20back%20taxes.%20Now%2C%20the%20agency%20said%20that%20it's%20collected%20%24122%20million%20from%20100%20of%20those%20taxpayers.%20That's%20a%20grand%20total%20of%20around%20%24160%20million%20clawed%20back%20from%20high-earners%2C%20according%20to%20Werfel%2C%20when%20combined%20with%20the%20%2438%20million%20that%20the%20IRS%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.irs.gov%2Fnewsroom%2Firs-announces-sweeping-effort-to-restore-fairness-to-tax-system-with-inflation-reduction-act-funding-new-compliance-efforts%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20collected%20from%20175%20high-earners%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20that's%20all%20without%20the%201%2C500%20other%20individuals%20that%20the%20IRS%20is%20working%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20funds%20that%20were%20collected%20should%20give%20you%20a%20fairly%20goo