h%20after%20his%20talks%20with%20Biden%2C%20you%20can%20understand%20that%20a%20very%20important%20decision%20was%20made.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20the%20decision%20included%20getting%20missiles%20with%20a%20longer%20range%2C%20Kuleba%20replied%3A%20%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20it%20means%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Kyiv%20Post%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKuleba%20did%20not%20say%20how%20many%20longer-range%20missiles%20he%20expects%20to%20arrive%2C%20or%20when.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20has%20not%20announced%20additional%20shipments%20of%20ATACMS%20to%20Ukraine%2C%20though%20it%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F10%2F17%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fukraine-atacms-attacks-russia.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ealso%20did%20not%20announce%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20previous%20shipment%20in%20advance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%2020%20ATACMS%20were%20sent%20to%20Ukraine%20in%20the%20first%20shipment%2C%20Western%20officials%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F10%2F17%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fukraine-atacms-attacks-russia.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20The%20New%20York%20Times%C2%A0this%20week%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine%20has%20continued%20to%20ask%20its%20allies%20for%20more%20advanced%20and%20longer-range%20weapons%20to%20aid%20in%20its%20defense%20against%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-new-atacms-missiles-go-twice-far-official-russia-airfields-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697806316000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653254dc96f7540cd061495c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-new-atacms-missiles-go-twice-far-official-russia-airfields-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ukraine%20likely%20used%20ATACMS%20missiles%20it%20got%20fro