n%20the%20craft%20of%20pottery%20have%20also%20been%20connected%20to%20these%20schemes%20but%20have%20found%20find%20little%20support%20in%20their%20livelihood%2C%20or%20in%20terms%20of%20protecting%20the%20craft.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20initiatives%20include%20a%20broad%20spectrum%20of%20objectives%2C%20from%20skill%20upgradation%20to%20facilitating%20the%20market%20for%20their%20final%20products.%20Falling%20under%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Micro%2C%20Small%20and%20Medium%20Enterprises%20(MSME)%2C%20pottery%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20cherished%20and%20prioritised%20craft%20among%20all.%20Or%20so%20they%20say.%20While%20the%20expansion%20of%20these%20initiatives%20seems%20promising%20in%20theory%2C%20the%20on-ground%20reality%20offers%20a%20contrasting%20perspective.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOver%20the%20past%20few%20months%2C%20field%20researchers%20as%20part%20of%20an%20ethnographic%20project%20undertaken%20by%20the%20Centre%20for%20New%20Economics%20Studies%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40centreforneweconomicsstudi8523%2Fplaylists%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EVisual%20Storyboard%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20team%20made%20an%20attempt%20to%20interact%20with%20the%20masters%2C%20craftspeople%2C%20and%20entrepreneurs%20of%20Uttam%20Nagar%E2%80%99s%20potter%20colony.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIn%20the%20long%20search%20of%20%E2%80%98actual%E2%80%99%20government%20support%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20our%20researchers%20asked%20the%20respondents%20whether%20they%20had%20received%20any%20assistance%20from%20the%20government%2C%20we%20received%20a%20unanimous%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eno%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Notably%2C%20the%20schemes%20available%20to%20these%20potters%20were%20limited%20to%20the%20ones%20designated%20for%20individuals%20below%20the%20poverty%20line.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENonetheless%2C%20it%20is%20incredibly%20vital%20to%20emphasise%20the%20stark%20absence%20of%20knowledge%20regarding%20the%20schemes%20made%20for%20them%20specifically.%20%E2%80%9CI%20personally%20feel%20that%20the%20government%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20offer%20us%20any%20assistance%2C%20not%20even%20a%20rupee.%20Here%20in%20our%20community%2C%20all%20of%20us%20are%20self-reliant%20and%20dedicated%20to%20sustaining%20our%20businesses%2C%20regardless%20of%20whether%20we%20gain%20a%20profit%20or%20incur%20losses.%20We%20rarely%20seek%20external%20help%20or%20support%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Narendra%20Kumar%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Kumhar%20Gram.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20absolutely%20no%20government%20schemes%20that%20offer%20us%20any%20form%20of%20assistance.%20Whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20covering%20our%20electricity%20bills%20or%20medical%20expenses%20at%20hospitals%2C%20we%E2%80%99re%20on%20our%20own.%20In%20case%20of%20medical%20emergencies%2C%20we%20resort%20to%20private%20hospitals%20which%20can%20be%20quite%20costly.%20Government%20hospitals%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20are%20overcrowded%20and%20busy%2C%20making%20it%20nearly%20impossible%20for%20us%20to%20access%20their%20services.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fbaked-in-the-sun-consumed-by-the-smoke-the-potters-of-delhis-kumhar-gram%5C%22%3EBaked%20In%20The%20Sun%2C%20Consumed%20By%20The%20Smoke%3A%20The%20Potters%20Of%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Kumhar%20Gram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhy%20is%20there%20such%20a%20significant%20disparity%20between%20the%20schemes%20that%20come%20from%20the%20government%20and%20those%20that%20reach%20the%20supposed%20beneficiaries%3F%20This%20is%20a%20classic%20%E2%80%98hope%20vs%20reality%E2%80%99%20conundrum%20that%20many%20potters%20fail%20to%20fathom.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20our%20team%20inquired%20further%2C%20we%20realised%20that%20a%20significant%20part%20of%20the%20issue%20was%20unawareness%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20stemmed%20from%20issues%20related%20to%20accessibility.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIneffective%20enforcement%20of%20a%20scheme%20and%20unsupportive%20officials%20exacerbate%20the%20anxieties%20within%20the%20community.%20Difficulty%20in%20acquiring%20loans%20is%20one%20of%20the%20ways%20in%20which%20this%20problem%20manifests.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENarendra%20Kumar%2C%20dubbed%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98terracotta%20%3Cem%3Eguru%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0within%20the%20community%2C%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CTill%20now%2C%20there%20has%20been%20little%20to%20no%20help%20from%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20end%20to%20help%20us%20acquire%20loans.%20It%20almost%20seems%20like%20we%2C%20the%20entire%20community%20of%20Uttam%20Nagar%2C%20have%20been%20blacklisted%20by%20the%20banks.%20Banks%20frequently%20decline%20our%20loan%20applications%20without%20providing%20any%20valid%20justification.%20Private%20banks%20still%20might%20give%20us%20a%20loan%20after%20looking%20at%20our%20business%2C%20but%20we%20have%20no%20such%20hopes%20from%20public%20banks.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20asked%20to%20elaborate%20on%20the%20alleged%20blacklisting%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20exact%20cause%20of%20our%20blacklisting%20remains%20unclear.%20It%20could%20be%20due%20to%20a%20past%20instance%20where%20someone%20from%20our%20community%20may%20have%20defaulted%20on%20a%20loan.%20Another%20contributing%20factor%20may%20be%20that%20all%20of%20us%20who%20reside%20here%20have%20purchased%20and%20settled%20on%20the%20land%20independently%2C%20as%20it%20is%20not%20a%20government-designated%20colony.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EEnvironmental%20concerns%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20one%20hand%2C%20national%20award%20winning%20potter%20Girraj%20Prasad%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.babushahi.com%2Ffull-news.php%3Fid%3D170846%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehas%20garnered%20recognition%20by%20exhibiting%20terracotta%20craft%20at%20the%20G20%20Crafts%20Bazaar%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20on%20the%20other%2C%20the%20community%20of%20potters%20residing%20in%20Uttam%20Nagar%20are%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fphotos%2Findia-news%2Fngt-pollution-ban-looms-large-over-delhi-potter-s-colony%2Fphoto-NEqhZvsGfXg0GpRgVDdRmI-3.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%20the%20edge%20of%20losing%20their%20livelihood%20over%20pollution%20concerns.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20potters%E2%80%99%20colony%20with%20its%20visible%20smoke%20is%20an%20obvious%20target%20because%20Delhi%20is%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20pollution%20problem.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFrequently%20under%20the%20national%20green%20tribunal%E2%80%99s%20(NGT%E2%80%99s)%20scanner%20for%20contributing%20to%20air%20pollution%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20the%20community%20has%20something%20different%20to%20say%20about%20the%20%E2%80%98harms%E2%80%99%20caused%20by%20the%20fumes.%20Ramesh%20Kumar%20(50)%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20and%20even%20grandfather%2C%20worked%20in%20the%20same%20industry%20for%20several%20decades%20and%20they%20have%20never%20faced%20any%20health%20issues%20due%20to%20the%20work.%20Since%20we%20do%20not%20use%20any%20chemical%2C%20the%20smoke%20isn%E2%80%99t%20harmful.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20151307%2FScreenshot-2023-10-20-at-3.05.30-PM.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20151307%2FScreenshot-2023-10-20-at-3.05.30-PM.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20151307%2FScreenshot-2023-10-20-at-3.05.30-PM-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20151307%2FScreenshot-2023-10-20-at-3.05.30-PM-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681043%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPotter%E2%80%99s%20colony%20in%20Uttam%20Nagar.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20they%20employ%20clay%20ovens%20or%20kilns%20that%20are%20fueled%20by%20burning%20wood%20husk%20and%20cow%20dung%2C%20the%20potters%20assert%20that%20their%20production%20method%20may%20be%20regarded%20as%20entirely%20organic.%20On%20each%20side%20of%20the%20lane%20are%20dwellings%20made%20of%20clay%2C%20and%20the%20streets%20are%20covered%20in%20heaps%20of%20it.%20A%20certain%20family%20is%20responsible%20for%20each%20mound.%20The%20majority%20of%20the%20homes%20have%20two%20stories%2C%20and%20virtually%20all%20of%20them%20have%20kilns%2C%20either%20within%20or%20protruding%20from%20a%20higher%20story.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20further%20inquiry%2C%20Pradeep%20Kumar%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20smoke%20that%20comes%20out%20of%20wood%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20harm%20a%20human%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20rubber%20and%20chemicals%20that%20do.%20We%20only%20burn%20wood%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eburadda%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(wood%20flakes)%2C%20so%20it%E2%80%99s%20not%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbad%E2%80%9D%20smoke%20that%20comes%20as%20a%20by-product.%20Oil-based%20fire%20is%20harmful%20as%20well.%20There%E2%80%99s%20more%20dangerous%20smoke%20that%20gets%20released%20during%20stubble%20burning%20and%20forest%20fires%2C%20but%20no%20one%20talks%20about%20that.%20These%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebhattis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(kilns)%20are%20our%20livelihood%2C%20and%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20believe%20that%20an%20hour%20of%20us%20baking%20our%20products%20causes%20any%20damage.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20evident%20by%20the%20precarious%20conditions%20of%20the%20potters%20it%20is%20not%20really%20their%20voices%20and%20concerns%20that%20are%20shaping%20these%20%E2%80%98reformatory%20policies.%E2%80%99%20They%20are%20the%20voices%20of%20the%201990s%20liberalisation%20policies%20which%20had%20the%20goal%20of%20making%20Delhi%20a%20metropolis%20of%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20the%20potters%E2%80%99%20village%E2%80%99s%20future%20is%20unknown%2C%20there%20is%20no%20indication%20of%20unfavourable%20unrest%20on%20the%20streets.%20Every%20year%2C%20the%20months%20leading%20up%20to%20Diwali%20are%20their%20busiest%20and%20business%20is%20brisk%20because%20in%20addition%20to%20serving%20the%20Indian%20market%2C%20they%20also%20export%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ediyas%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20nations%20with%20sizable%20Indian%20diasporas%2C%20like%20Australia%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Canada%2C%20and%20Singapore.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20there%20being%20a%20tremendous%20demand%20for%20their%20craft%20during%20the%20festive%20season%2C%20uncertainty%20continues%20to%20surround%20their%20livelihood.%20With%20the%20time%20commitment%20that%20the%20craft%20requires%2C%20it%20is%20unavoidably%20challenging%20for%20the%20artisans%20to%20chase%20behind%20every%20new%20policy%20and%20law%20reform.%20In%20the%20small%20alleys%20with%20mounds%20of%20mud%20and%20half-baked%20pots%2C%20there%20is%20also%20a%20general%20sense%20of%20unawareness%20and%20disunity%20attributable%20to%20their%20socio-economic%20backgrounds%2C%20historical%20and%20systematic%20marginalisation%2C%20and%20a%20pressure%20to%20make%20ends%20meet.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUnder%20such%20circumstances%2C%20the%20site%20of%20research%20for%20collecting%20data%20and%20policy-making%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmonoskop.org%2Fimages%2F4%2F4e%2FSaid_Edward_Orientalism_1979.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eas%20Edward%20Said%20would%20argue%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20should%20refrain%20from%20the%20shadows%20of%20an%20institution%20that%20%E2%80%98makes%20statements%20about%20it%20%5Bthe%20orient%5D%2C%20authorising%20views%20of%20it%2C%20describing%20it%2C%20by%20teaching%20about%20it%2C%20settling%20it%2C%20ruling%20over%20it.%E2%80%99%20Instead%2C%20a%20complexly%20situated%20community%20of%20vulnerable%20artisans%20desires%20a%20body%20of%20knowledge%20that%20acknowledges%20the%20significance%20of%20their%20perspectives%20and%20attempts%20to%20account%20for%20how%2C%20and%20why%2C%20such%20perspectives%20may%20have%20developed%3B%20that%20would%20eventually%20affect%20the%20ability%20of%20the%20community%20to%20avail%20a%20positive%20flow%20of%20rights.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20artisans%20of%20India%2C%20we%20are%20far%20away%20from%20the%20realisation%20of%20rights%20that%20lead%20to%20the%20enhancement%20of%20their%20capabilities%2C%20and%20more%20importantly%2C%20provide%20meaning%20and%20purpose%20in%20their%20efforts%20to%20practice%20and%20conserve%20the%20craft.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3EThis%20is%20the%20second%20article%20of%20a%20two-part%20series%20from%20CNES%E2%80%99%20Visual%20Storyboard%20team%20from%20a%20field%20project%20focusing%20on%20the%20lives-livelihoods%20of%20West%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20pottery%20makers%20and%20their%20endangered%20craft.%20You%20can%20read%20the%20first%20part%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fculture%2Fbaked-in-the-sun-consumed-by-the-smoke-the-potters-of-delhis-kumhar-gram%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cb%3ETavleen%20Kaur%3C%2Fb%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20Senior%20Research%20Assis