C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20CoreLogic%20Case-Shiller%20Index%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20recent%20pullback%20in%20supply%20could%20push%20them%20upward%20in%20the%20weeks%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20think%20in%20the%20very%20short%20term%20that%20provides%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20upward%20pressure%20on%20home%20prices%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20James%20Egan%2C%20Morgan%20Stanley's%20co-head%20of%20securitized%20research%2C%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2023-10-19%2Fhere-s-what-8-mortgage-rates-will-do-to-the-housing-market%3Fsrnd%3Doddlots%26leadSource%3Duverify%2520wall%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecent%20episode%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Bloomberg's%20%26quot%3BOdd%20Lots%26quot%3B%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20team's%20base%20case%20is%20that%20prices%20remain%20flat%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20year%2C%20they're%20moving%20toward%20their%20bull%20case%20of%20a%205%25%20increase%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20investment%20bank's%20models%20indicate%20that%20if%20housing%20supply%20grows%20by%20just%205%25%20next%20year%2C%20mortgage%20rates%20don't%20come%20down%2C%20and%20sales%20and%20transaction%20volumes%20remain%20flat%2C%20then%20home%20prices%20could%20fall%20by%205%25in%202024%2C%20Egan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMortgage%20rates%20have%20surged%20from%20about%203%25%20to%208%25%20in%20under%20two%20years%2C%20which%20has%20led%20prospective%20sellers%20who've%20locked%20in%20cheap%2C%20fixed-rate%20mortgages%20to%20balk%20at%20listing%20their%20homes.%20There's%20also%20been%20insufficient%20homebuilding%20over%20the%20last%2015%20years%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20shortfall%20of%20as%20many%20as%206%20million%20homes%2C%20Egan%20said%20on%20the%20podcast.%20Those%20two%20trends%20mean%20there's%20a%20shortage%20of%20homes%20for%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20jump%20in%20mortgage%20rates%20has%20priced%20out%20many%20buyers%20who%20aren't%20willing%20or%20able%20to%20pay%20top%20dollar%20for%20their%20next%20home%20and%20take%20on%20onerously%20large%20monthly%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20dealing%20with%20kind%20of%20a%20big%20headwind%20and%20a%20big%20tailwind%20at%20the%20same%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Egan%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20pressures%20on%20housing%20supply%20and%20demand.%20He%20expects%20mortgage%20rates%20to%20come%20down%20by%20the%20middle%20of%20next%20year%2C%20and%20prices%20to%20come%20under%20pressure%20if%20they%20don't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20medium%20term%2C%20if%20rates%20stay%20at%20these%20levels%2C%20we%20think%20the%20demand%20will%20remain%20pretty%20tepid%2C%20which%20means%20that%20we%20are%20reliant%20upon%20supply%20remaining%20near%20historic%20lows%20to%20keep%20home%20prices%20at%20these%20levels%2C%26quot%3B%20Egan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEgan%20added%20that%20steep%20mortgage%20rates%20also%20weigh%20on%20housing%20starts%2C%20and%20can%20have%20wider%20impacts%20on%20the%20economy%20because%20people%20spend%20less%20money%20buying%20homes%20and%20preparing%20their%20homes%20for%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMortgage%20rates%20have%20jumped%20largely%20because%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20has%20raised%20its%20benchmark%20interest%20rates%20from%20virtually%20zero%20to%20more%20than%205%25%20since%20last%20spring.%20The%20central%20bank%20has%20raised%20borrowing%20costs%20to%20combat%20inflation%2C%20which%20hit%20a%2040-year%20high%20of%20over%209%25%20last%20summer%2C%20but%20has%20slowed%20to%20below%204%25%20in%20recent%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhousing-market-home-prices-affordability-crisis-mortgage-rates-morgan-stanley-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697803822000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6524ae3a6561dd877e75