ing%20across%20the%20Middle%20East%20over%20Israel's%20strikes%20in%20Gaza%2C%20China%20and%20Russia%20are%20finding%20common%20cause%20with%20countries%20across%20the%20region%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Palestinians.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFor%20Moscow%20and%20Beijing%2C%20Israel's%20bombardment%20of%20Gaza%20following%20the%20Hamas%20attacks%20that%20killed%201%2C400%20Israelis%20presents%20an%20opportunity%20to%20burnish%20their%20credentials%20as%20the%20champions%20of%20the%20developing%20world%2C%20in%20contrast%20with%20the%20United%20States%2C%20which%20has%20put%20its%20support%20squarely%20behind%20ally%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20consistently%20called%20for%20restraint%20and%20a%20ceasefire%20but%20has%20also%20sharpened%20its%20criticism%20of%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsrael's%20actions%20have%20gone%20beyond%20the%20scope%20of%20self-defence%2C%26quot%3B%20Chinese%20Foreign%20Minister%20Wang%20Yi%20said%20this%20week%2C%20calling%20on%20it%20to%20stop%20its%20%26quot%3Bcollective%20punishment%26quot%3B%20of%20Gaza%20residents%2C%20Chinese%20state%20media%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERussia%20has%20expressed%20sympathy%20for%20the%20Palestinians%20while%20blaming%20the%20US%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20many%20people%20will%20agree%20with%20me%20that%20this%20is%20a%20vivid%20example%20of%20the%20failure%20of%20United%20States%20policy%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%26quot%3B%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20said%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20Putin%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20have%20sought%20to%20deepen%20ties%20to%20the%20global%20south%2C%20seeing%20economic%20opportunities%20and%20possibly%20a%20way%20to%20counterbalance%20the%20diplomatic%20influence%20of%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20on%20display%20this%20week%20as%20China%20hosted%20a%20summit%20for%20Xi's%20signature%20Belt%20and%20Road%20Initiative%2C%20which%20has%20lent%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20for%20infrastructure%20projects%20across%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20Africa%2C%20Latin%20America%20and%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPutin%20attended%20and%20met%20Xi%20for%20three%20hours%20of%20talks%20that%20included%20%26quot%3Ban%20in-depth%20exchange%20of%20views%20on%20the%20Palestinian-Israeli%20situation%26quot%3B%2C%20China%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina%20and%20Russia%20still%20see%20(the%20crisis)%20more%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20United%20States%20than%20in%20terms%20of%20either%20Palestine%20or%20Israel%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jon%20Alterman%2C%20director%20of%20the%20Middle%20East%20Program%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%20in%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20United%20States%20can%20effectively%20rally%20the%20world%2C%20it's%20bad%20for%20them.%20If%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20grow%20increasingly%20isolated%2C%20they%20see%20that%20as%20good%20for%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESupport%20For%20Palestine%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20strategies%20of%20Russia%20and%20China%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20are%20not%20fully%20aligned%20they%20have%20much%20in%20common.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERussia%20is%20sharply%20critical%20of%20the%20US%20but%20China%20has%20mostly%20avoided%20criticising%20it%2C%20a%20contrast%20to%20early%20in%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20when%20China's%20support%20of%20Russia%20turned%20an%20unwelcome%20spotlight%20on%20its%20diplomatic%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChina%20signalled%20its%20growing%20influence%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20this%20year%20when%20it%20announced%20a%20surprise%20deal%20on%20the%20restoration%20of%20ties%20between%20Saudi%20Arabia%20and%20Iran.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERussia%20too%20has%20been%20improving%20ties%20with%20Iran%2C%20which%20has%20included%20supplies%20of%20Iranian%20drones%20and%20common%20cause%20in%20backing%20Syrian%20President%20Bashar%20al-Assad.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBoth%20China%20and%20Russia%20share%20a%20history%20of%20support%20for%20the%20Palestinians%20-%20and%20are%20critical%20of%20what%20they%20say%20is%20the%20marginalisation%20of%20them%20by%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20clearly%20a%20shared%20interest%20in%20emphasizing%20the%20negative%20role%20of%20the%20US%20in%20the%20conflict%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Jean-Loup%20Samaan%2C%20senior%20research%20fellow%20at%20the%20Middle%20East%20Institute%20of%20the%20National%20University%20of%20Singapore.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20fits%20within%20their%20broader%20narrative%20on%20the%20need%20to%20build%20an%20alternative%20world%20order%20to%20the%20US%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERussia's%20state%20media%20has%20said%20it%20was%20sending%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20Gaza%20and%20China%20has%20sent%20its%20Middle%20East%20envoy%20to%20the%20region%2C%20where%20he%20met%20Russia's%20special%20representative.%20Russia%20said%20on%20Thursday%20it%20was%20coordinating%20Middle%20East%20policy%20with%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Chinese%20media%20covered%20the%20Hamas%20attacks%20on%20October%207%2C%20since%20then%20reports%20have%20carried%20images%20of%20Palestinian%20suffering%2C%20with%20some%20prominently%20citing%20Palestinian%20sources%20as%20saying%20Israel%20was%20responsible.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNone%20of%20the%20reality%20that%20shocked%20much%20of%20the%20world%20on%20October%207%20is%20in%20Chinese%20news.%20Instead%2C%20the%20news%20features%20Israeli%20bombing%20of%20Gaza%20without%20explaining%20that%20the%20target%20is%20only%20Hamas%20infrastructure%2C%26quot%3B%20Carice%20Witte%2C%20director%20of%20the%20SIGNAL%20Group%2C%20a%20Sino-Israel%20relations%20think%20tank%20based%20in%20Tel%20Aviv.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESeeking%20Allies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%20%3Cp%3ERussia's%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20gives%20it%20an%20added%20incentive%20to%20align%20itself%20with%20the%20Palestinian%20cause.%3C%2Fp%