uts%20who%20can%20then%20have%20a%20mission%20of%20up%20to%20a%20week%20in%20a%20low%20earth%20orbit.%20The%20crew%20module%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20tested%20on%20a%20new%20rocket%20initially%20without%20housing%20any%20astronauts%20and%20an%20abort%20test%20will%20be%20conducted%20at%20an%20altitude%20of%2017%20kilometres%20and%20the%20crew%20module%20will%20be%20recovered%20from%20the%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20by%20the%20Indian%20Navy.%20Many%20tests%20like%20this%20will%20be%20conducted%20and%20if%20nearly%20two%20dozen%20or%20more%20of%20these%20big%20tests%20are%20successful%2C%20then%20any%20of%20the%20four%20designated%20astronauts%20will%20be%20flown.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGaganyaan%20Mission%20will%20launch%20an%20Indian%20astronaut%20into%20space%20from%20Sriharikota.%20Crew%20Escape%20System%20will%20be%20tested%20soon%20before%20humans%20can%20be%20flown.%20The%20module%20can%20accommodate%20a%20crew%20of%20three%20for%20about%20a%20week%20in%20space.%20The%20Crew%20Module%20has%20been%20designed%20by%20ISRO%20and%20it%20is%20Indian.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELaunch%20Vehicle%20Mark%20-3%20the%20chosen%20rocket%20is%20now%20human-rated.%20Four%20astronauts%20have%20been%20trained%2C%20all%20four%20are%20Indian%20Air%20Force%20(IAF)%20test%20pilots%20and%20all%20four%20in%20the%20maiden%20cohort%20are%20men%20as%20there%20were%20no%20female%20test%20pilots%20in%20India.%20Nair%20says%20%26quot%3BWomen%20can%20be%20accommodated%20in%20the%20future%20as%20ISRO%20is%20gender%20agnostic%20and%20only%20talent%20matters%26quot%3B.%20In%20the%20Gaganyaan%20Mission%2C%20Russian-made%20flight%20suits%20will%20be%20used%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20ISRO's%20ambitious%20Gaganyaan%20Mission%20to%20send%20an%20Indian%20astronaut%20into%20space%20is%20giving%20the%20scientists%20working%20on%20it%20sleepless%20nights%20since%20this%20will%20be%20the%20first%20time%20ISRO%20will%20launch%20an%20Indian%20into%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDr%20Unnikrishnan%20Nair%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20astronauts%20will%20bring%20glory%20to%20India%2C%20and%20if%20India%20succeeds%20it%20will%20become%20the%20fourth%20country%20to%20have%20independent%20capability%20to%20send%20humans%20to%20space%20after%20Russia%2C%20USA%20and%20China.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20tense%20about%20Gaganyaan%2C%20we%20need%20to%20do%20our%20homework%20properly%20but%20Gaganyaan%20will%20certainly%20cause%20skipping%20of%20heartbeats%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697802480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Faioufdp4_gaganyaan-mission-ani_625x300_20_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgaganyaan-in-mission-to-send-indian-to-moon-gaganyaans-1st-big-test-tomorrow-4499877%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Riding%20on%20the%20huge%20success%20of%20Chandrayaan-3%2C%20India%20is%20now%20taking%20baby%20steps%20towards%20the%20ambitious%20Gaganyaan%20mission.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgaganyaan-in-mission-to-send-indian-to-moon-gaganyaans-1st-big-test-tomorrow-4499877%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgaganyaan-in-mission-to-send-indian-to-moon-gaganyaans-1st-big-test-tomorrow-4499877%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgaganyaan-in-mission-to-send-indian-to-moon-gaganyaans-1st-big-test-tomorrow-4499877%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%20%7C%20Everything%20You%20Need%20to%20Know%20About%20Hamas%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20165049%2FKT-20-b.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20conflict%20enters%20its%2014th%20day%2C%20Karan%20Thapar%20interviews%20Paola%20Caridi%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20best%20informed%20and%20most%20highly%20regarded%20authorities%20on%20Hamas%20and%20the%20author%20of%20%3Cem%3EHamas%3A%20Resistance%20to%20Regime%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EJerusalem%20Without%20God%3A%20Portrait%20of%20a%20Cruel%20City%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20critical%20question%20is%3A%20%E2%80%98Do%20we%20know%20the%20truth%20about%20Hamas%3F%20And%20when%20we%20find%20out%2C%20will%20it%20surprise%20us%20or%20confirm%20the%20worst%3F%E2%80%99%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20emerges%20is%20a%20complex%20and%20indeed%20complicated%20picture%20that%20is%20not%20easy%20to%20grasp%20in%20terms%20of%20simple%20single%20sentences.%20Paola%20Caridi%20paints%20a%20multifaceted%20picture%20of%20Hamas.%20She%20says%20there%20are%20different%20divisions%20within%20Hamas%20(military%20and%20political)%20which%20are%20often%20at%20odds%20with%20each%20other.%20She%20believes%20that%20the%20October%207%20attack%20probably%20happened%20without%20the%20political%20division%20being%20aware%20or%20consulted.%20She%20also%20says%20that%20the%20top%20leadership%20of%20Hamas%20is%20outside%20Gaza%20i.e.%20abroad%20and%20increasingly%20cut%20off%20from%20what%20is%20happening%20in%20Gaza.%20She%20says%20there%20are%20also%20divisions%20between%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%20and%20Hamas%20organisations%20in%20other%20parts%2C%20not%20just%20the%20West%20Bank%20but%20elsewhere%20too.%20She%20says%20Hamas%20has%20evolved%20in%20what%20it%20stands%20for%20and%2C%20more%20importantly%2C%20how%20it%20views%20Israel%20but%20also%20gone%20back%20and%20reversed%20itself.%20In%201987%2C%20when%20it%20was%20founded%2C%20it%20was%20committed%20to%20the%20elimination%20of%20Israel%2C%20including%20physically.%20The%20first%20signs%20of%20compromise%20happened%20in%202006-07%2C%20when%20Hamas%20won%20power%20in%20Gaza%20and%20became%20part%20of%20the%20institutional%20structure%20of%20politics.%20Reversal%20began%20to%20happen%20in%202011%2C%20when%201%2C027%20Hamas%20prisoners%20were%20released%20from%20Israeli%20jails%20and%20their%20influence%20radicalised%20the%20organization.%20A%20second%20compromise%20was%20apparent%20when%20Hamas%20changed%20its%20charter%20in%202017%20and%20accepted%20a%20sort%20of%20compromise%20whereby%20it%20was%20willing%20to%20live%20side%20by%20side%20with%20Israel%20but%20not%20recognise%20the%20existence%20of%20Israel.%20Since%20then%2C%20a%20reverse%20radicalisation%20has%20been%20happening.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FWtGyBoVmbSI%3Fsi%3DJQrtKmoZryRQo4KH%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20a%20complicated%20and%20difficult%20story%2C%20particularly%20for%20those%20who%20do%20not%20know%20Hamas%20and%20its%20history%2C%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20different%20responses%20to%20Hamas%20and%20how%20the%20world%2C%20with%20its%20treatment%20of%20Hamas%2C%20has%20added%20to%20the%20complications.%20Paola%20Caridi%20attempts%20to%20explain%20all%20of%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPaola%20Caridi%20also%20discusses%20how%20popular%20Hamas%20is%20in%20Gaza%2C%20in%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20and%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20an%20idea%20or%20an%20organisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20is%20asked%20the%20following%20questions%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E1)%20Forgive%20me%20if%20my%20questions%20seem%20basic%20and%20even%20rudimentary%2C%20but%20in%20India%20we%20know%20very%20little%20about%20Hamas.%20So%20can%20I%20start%20by%20asking%20how%20would%20you%20characterise%20or%20describe%20this%20organisation%3F%20At%20the%20moment%20most%20governments%20and%20media%20organisations%20call%20it%20a%20terrorist%20organisation.%20From%20your%20perception%20would%20that%20be%20correct%20or%20mistaken%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E2)%20What%20is%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20ideology%3F%20What%20are%20the%20principles%20and%20goals%20it%20stands%20for%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E3)%20Now%20there%20are%20some%20reports%20that%20Israel%20has%20played%20a%20role%20in%20funding%20and%20supporting%20the%20founding%20of%20Hamas.%20I%20know%20that%20when%20he%20was%20military%20governor%20of%20Gaza%2C%20Gen%20Gonen%20Segev%20assisted%20and%20helped%20several%20religious%20based%20groups%20as%20a%20way%20of%20checking%20the%20secular%20PLO.%20Is%20that%20true%20of%20Hamas%20as%20well%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E4)%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20original%20charter%20commits%20the%20organisation%20to%20work%20for%20the%20destruction%20or%20elimination%20of%20Israel%20but%20was%20there%20a%20significant%20change%20in%202017%20whereby%20without%20recognising%20Israel%20Hamas%20was%20prepared%20to%20accept%20its%20existence%20as%20a%20state%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E5)%20Since%202017%2C%20how%20would%20you%20describe%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20attitude%20to%20Israel%20and%20how%20has%20it%20evolved%20between%202017%20and%202023%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E6)%20Hamas%20has%20fought%20several%20%E2%80%98wars%E2%80%99%20with%20Israel%20but%20the%20Israelis%20were%20convinced%20that%20for%20the%20last%20two%20years%20at%20least%20that%20Hamas%20was%20focused%20on%20the%20development%20of%20Gaza%20and%20was%20no%20longer%20committed%20to%20overthrowing%20Israel.%20How%20serious%20a%20misreading%20of%20reality%20was%20that%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E7)%20Do%20we%20know%20the%20specific%20reasons%20why%20Hamas%20launched%20this%20massive%20attack%20on%20October%207%3F%20And%20secondly%20what%20message%20was%20it%20sending%20by%20choosing%20the%2050th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20Yom%20Kippur%20war%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E8)%20How%20popular%20is%20Hamas%20in%20Gaza%3F%20We%E2%80%99re%20often%20told%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20represent%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20but%20does%20it%20or%20does%20it%20not%20represent%20the%20people%20of%20Gaza%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E9)%20And%20what%20about%20the%20Palestinians%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%3F%20How%20do%20they%20view%20Hamas%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E10)%20Is%20Hamas%20misunderstood%20by%20the%20West%3F%20Even%20if%20understandable%2C%20is%20it%20seen%20through%20Israeli%20eyes%2C%20which%20are%20inevitably%20distorting%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E11)%20Is%20Hamas%20locked%20in%20a%20war%20with%20Israel%20that%20cannot%20be%20mediated%20and%20resolved%3F%20Or%20could%20Hamas%20agree%20to%20a%20two%20state%20solution%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E12)%20Finally%20and%20I%E2%80%99ve%20deliberately%20left%20this%20to%20the%20end.%20Can%20Hamas%20be%20obliterated%20as%20Israel%20insists%3F%20In%20other%20words%20is%20it%20an%20idea%20or%20an%20organisation%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E13)%20If%20it%E2%80%99s%20true%20that%20the%20Hamas%20security%20head%20has%20been%20killed%2C%20as%20the%20Palestine%20Authority%20has%20said%2C%20how%20serious%20a%20blow%20would%20this%20be%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E14)%20To%20what%20extent%20has%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%E2%80%99s%20handling%20of%20the%20Palestine%20situation%20over%20the%20last%2015%20years%20he%E2%80%99s%20been%20prime%20minister%20made%20matters%20worse%20by%20adding%20to%20the%20problems%20with%20Hamas%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E15)%20Are%20there%20realists%20in%20Hamas%20who%20can%20identify%20what%20they%20can%20live%20with%20as%20a%20practical%20solution%3F%20It%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20everything%20they%20want%20but%20are%20there%20Hamas%20realists%20who%20agree%20on%20an%20outcome%20Israel%20can%20accept%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697802335000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20165049%2FKT-20-b.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fvideo%2Fwatch-hamas-karan-thapar-paola-caridi-interview%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20an%20interview%20with%20Karan%20Thapar%2C%20Paola%20Caridi%2C%20the%20of%20author%20'Hamas%3A%20Resistance%20to%20Regime'%2C%20paints%20a%20complex%20and%20indeed%20complicated%20picture%20of%20the%20organisation%20responsible%20for%20the%20deadly%20October%207%20attack%20on%20Israel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22http