o%20a%20comfortable%20victory%20over%20Bangladesh%20in%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20on%20Thursday%20but%20a%20controversial%20decision%20by%20umpire%20Richard%20Kettleborough%20became%20a%20major%20talking%20point%20after%20the%20match.%20With%20Kohli%20batting%20on%2097%20and%20India%20needing%20two%20runs%20to%20win%2C%20Bangladesh%20bowler%20Nasum%20Ahmed%20fired%20a%20delivery%20towards%20the%20leg%20stump.%20Kohli%20shuffled%20a%20bit%20towards%20the%20stumps%20and%20the%20wicket-keeper%20collected%20it%20on%20the%20leg%20side.%20However%2C%20the%20umpire%20decided%20to%20not%20award%20a%20wide%20to%20India%20and%20instead%2C%20the%20delivery%20was%20judged%20to%20be%20a%20dot%20ball.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKohli%20went%20on%20to%20score%20his%2048th%20ODI%20century%20with%20a%20massive%20six%20just%20two%20balls%20after%20this%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20fans%20were%20left%20confused%20by%20the%20umpire's%20decision%20to%20not%20award%20the%20wide%20despite%20the%20wicket-keeper%20collecting%20the%20ball%20on%20the%20leg%20side%2C%20the%20reason%20was%20a%20rule%20change%20by%20Marylebone%20Cricket%20Club%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20modern%20game%2C%20batters%20are%2C%20more%20than%20ever%2C%20moving%20laterally%20around%20the%20crease%20before%20the%20ball%20is%20bowled.%20It%20was%20felt%20unfair%20that%20a%20delivery%20might%20be%20called%20%E2%80%98Wide'%20if%20it%20passes%20where%20the%20batter%20had%20stood%20as%20the%20bowler%20entered%20his%2Fher%20delivery%20stride.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTherefore%2C%20Law%2022.1%20has%20been%20amended%20so%20that%20a%20Wide%20will%20apply%20to%20where%20the%20batter%20is%20standing%2C%20where%20the%20striker%20has%20stood%20at%20any%20point%20since%20the%20bowler%20began%20their%20run-up%2C%20and%20which%20would%20also%20have%20passed%20wide%20of%20the%20striker%20in%20a%20normal%20batting%20position%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20amended%20rule%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20rule%20was%20brought%20in%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20bowlers%20are%20not%20punished%20for%20batters%20moving%20across%20the%20stumps%20just%20when%20the%20ball%20is%20delivered.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20Kohli's%20batting%20stance%20kept%20him%20outside%20the%20line%20of%20the%20leg%20stump%20and%20when%20he%20shuffled%20across%2C%20the%20umpire%20judged%20it%20to%20be%20a%20change%20of%20position%20by%20the%20batter.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697802240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Ftostkqog_virat_625x300_20_October_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fnew-mcc-rule-that-may-have-helped-virat-kohli-score-his-48th-odi-ton-explained-4499683%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20controversial%20decision%20by%20umpire%20Richard%20Kettleborough%20involving%20Virat%20Kohli%20became%20a%20major%20talking%20point%20after%20the%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20match%20between%20India%20and%20Bangladesh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fnew-mcc-rule-that-may-have-helped-virat-kohli-score-his-48th-odi-ton-explained-4499683%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fnew-mcc-rule-that-may-have-helped-virat-kohli-score-his-48th-odi-ton-explained-4499683%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fnew-mcc-rule-that-may-have-helped-virat-kohli-score-his-48th-odi-ton-explained-4499683%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Money%20laundering%3A%20Sanjay%20Singh's%20plea%20dismissed%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697802053000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104584768%2Cimgsize-669276.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fmoney-laundering-case-delhi-hc-