ective.%20Notably%2C%20the%20suggestion%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20chief%20minister%20for%20an%20all-party%20meeting%20signals%20a%20concerted%20effort%20to%20address%20the%20potential%20ramifications%20of%20the%20survey%E2%80%99s%20findings.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20itself%20provides%20crucial%20insights%20into%20the%20demographic%20makeup%20of%20Bihar.%20The%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%20and%20Extremely%20Backward%20Castes%20(EBCs)%20collectively%20constitute%20a%20significant%2063%25%2C%20with%20Scheduled%20Castes%20(SCs)%20making%20up%2019.65%25%20of%20the%20population.%20The%20upper%20castes%2C%20including%20the%20general%20category%2C%20along%20with%20around%205%25%20of%20upper%20caste%20Muslims%2C%20comprise%2015.52%25.%20This%20underscores%20the%20intricate%20socio-political%20landscape%20of%20Bihar%2C%20a%20complexity%20that%20the%20BJP%20navigates%20in%20its%20pursuit%20of%20inclusive%20representation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EGiven%20this%20context%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99%20meticulous%20consideration%20of%20the%20survey%E2%80%99s%20findings%20underscores%20its%20commitment%20to%20inclusive%20governance.%20It%20is%20imperative%20for%20political%20parties%20to%20transcend%20divisive%20rhetoric%20and%20grapple%20with%20the%20realities%20that%20shape%20the%20lives%20of%20the%20people%20they%20represent.%20This%20endeavour%20holds%20particular%20relevance%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Pasmanda%20outreach%20efforts.%20The%20census%20thus%20serves%20as%20a%20platform%20for%20fostering%20inclusivity%20and%20promoting%20a%20more%20comprehensive%20understanding%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20diverse%20populace.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20trail%20of%20hate%20crimes%3A%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20own%20members%20undermine%20Pasmanda%20engagement%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20purported%20outreach%20to%20the%20Pasmanda%20Muslims%20is%20marred%20by%20a%20grim%20reality%20%E2%80%93%20a%20trail%20of%20hate%20crimes%20committed%20or%20endorsed%20by%20its%20own%20members.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Feditorial-bilkis-bano-justice%5C%22%3EBilkis%20Bano%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Pasmanda%20Muslim%2C%20endured%20a%20nightmarish%20ordeal%20during%20the%202002%20Gujarat%20riots%2C%20where%20she%20and%20her%20three-year-old%20daughter%20fell%20victim%20to%20a%20violent%20mob%2C%20resulting%20in%2014%20tragic%20deaths.%20Shockingly%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20later%20sanctioned%20the%20release%20of%2011%20individuals%20convicted%20for%20their%20roles%20in%20this%20gruesome%20incident.%20In%20another%20harrowing%20incident%20in%202019%2C%20Tabrez%20Ansari%2C%20a%20Pasmanda%20Muslim%2C%20was%20ruthlessly%20lynched%20and%20coerced%20to%20recite%20Hindu%20religious%20slogans%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20a%20state%20where%20the%20BJP%20has%20support.%20Moreover%2C%20the%20garlands%20bestowed%20by%20former%20Union%20Minister%20Jayant%20Sinha%20upon%20eight%20individuals%20convicted%20of%20lynching%20in%20Ramgarh%20cast%20a%20sinister%20shadow.%20Among%20the%20victims%20in%20this%20case%20was%20Alimuddin%20Ansari%2C%20a%20Pasmanda%20man.%20These%20distressing%20episodes%20lay%20bare%20the%20formidable%20challenge%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Pasmanda%20outreach%20faces%20from%20within%20the%20community%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F18211149%2Fimage-330.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F18211149%2Fimage-330.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F18211149%2Fimage-330-300x138.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F08%2F18211149%2Fimage-330-1024x472.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-614505%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22553%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPeople%20convicted%20for%20rape%20and%20murder%20in%20the%20Bilkis%20Bano%20case%20of%20the%202002%20Gujarat%20riots%2C%20being%20welcomed%20as%20they%20come%20out%20of%20the%20Godhra%20sub-jail%20after%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20allowed%20their%20release%20under%20its%20remission%20policy%2C%20in%20Godhra%2C%20August%2015%2C%202022.%20Photo%3A%20PTI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAli%20Anwar%20Ansari%E2%80%99s%20Vision%20of%20Pasmanda%3A%20A%20Call%20for%20Collective%20Empowerment%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBefore%20delving%20into%20the%20dynamics%20of%20Pasmanda%20politics%2C%20it%20is%20imperative%20to%20comprehend%20the%20essence%20of%20Pasmanda.%20In%20an%20insightful%20interview%2C%20Ali%20Anwar%20Ansari%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Pasmanda%20Muslim%20Mahaz%20and%20former%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%2C%20sheds%20light%20on%20the%20significance%20of%20%E2%80%98Pasmanda%E2%80%99%20as%20a%20unifying%20concept.%20He%20starkly%20contrasts%20it%20with%20the%20divisive%20policies%20championed%20by%20the%20BJP.%20Ansari%20astutely%20emphasises%20that%20%E2%80%98Pasmanda%E2%80%99%20transcends%20religious%20boundaries%2C%20encompassing%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20alike%2C%20thereby%20challenging%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20narrow%20sectarian%20approach.%20His%20unwavering%20commitment%20arises%20from%20the%20belief%20that%20marginalised%20communities%2C%20akin%20to%20Dalits%20and%20backward%20classes%2C%20can%20only%20truly%20thrive%20through%20collective%20empowerment.%20Ansari%20fervently%20advocates%20for%20a%20united%20front%2C%20bringing%20together%20Hindu%20Dalits%2C%20Sikhs%20and%20Christians%20to%20counter%20the%20entrenched%20power%20structures%20perpetuated%20by%20the%20BJP%20over%20generations.%20In%20this%20singular%2C%20resonant%20term%2C%20%E2%80%98Pasmanda%E2%80%99%2C%20lies%20the%20potential%20to%20rally%20a%20diverse%20multitude%2C%20challenging%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20divisive%20tactics%20and%20championing%20a%20more%20inclusive%2C%20equitable%20future%20for%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20recent%20overtures%20to%20Pasmanda%20Muslims%2C%20a%20marginalised%20subset%20within%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20have%20sparked%20heated%20debate%20in%20Indian%20politics.%20The%20party%E2%80%99s%20attempts%20to%20bridge%20this%20divide%20raise%20questions%20about%20their%20true%20intentions.%20This%20outreach%20unfolds%20against%20a%20backdrop%20of%20escalating%20communal%20tensions%20and%20contentious%20policies%2C%20further%20complicating%20the%20assessment%20of%20its%20sincerity.%20As%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20loom%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Minority%20Morcha%20gears%20up%20for%20a%20targeted%20outreach%20program%20focused%20on%20the%20Pasmanda%20community.%20Senior%20party%20officials%20have%20also%20been%20tasked%20with%20this.%20While%20this%20manoeuvre%20may%20appear%20strategic%2C%20it%20raises%20legitimate%20concerns%20about%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20approach%20to%20minority%20engagement%2C%20given%20the%20enduring%20political%20significance%20of%20the%20Muslim%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIntra-religious%20divisions%3A%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20tactical%20approach%20to%20Muslim%20communities%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIrfan%20Engineer%E2%80%99s%20analysis%20dissects%20the%20multifaceted%20divisions%20within%20the%20Muslim%20community%2C%20spanning%20Wahabis%2C%20Deobandis%2C%20Ahle-Hadis%2C%20Bohras%2C%20Khojas%2C%20Memons%2C%20and%20others.%20Each%20group%20claims%20fervent%20devotion%20and%20piety%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20mosaic%20of%20religious%20identities.%20Additionally%2C%20Muslims%20segregate%20along%20geographical%2C%20social%2C%20and%20caste%20lines%2C%20including%20Sheikhs%2C%20Ansaris%2C%20Qureshis%2C%20Pathans%2C%20Syeds%2C%20and%20Bagwans.%20Beyond%20their%20shared%20Islamic%20faith%2C%20these%20communities%20bear%20little%20sociological%20commonality.%20They%20seldom%20interact%20and%20fiercely%20guard%20their%20respective%20identities%2C%20with%20each%20sect%20maintaining%20its%20own%20mosque.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20schisms%20with%20other%20sects%2C%20notably%20Sunnis%2C%20Bohras%2C%20Khojas%2C%20Shias%2C%20and%20Sufis%20have%20gravitated%20towards%20BJP%20support.%20This%20prompts%20the%20BJP%20to%20concentrate%20efforts%20on%20minority%20Muslim%20communities%2C%20capitalising%20on%20existing%20intra-religious%20divisions.%20The%20BJP%20strategically%20avoids%20aligning%20with%20the%20orthodox%20Deobandis%2C%20as%20it%20risks%20alienating%20its%20core%20Hindutva%20base.%20Sufis%2C%20practising%20a%20more%20liberal%20interpretation%20of%20Islam%2C%20incorporate%20local%20Hindu%20customs%2C%20yielding%20a%20unique%20blend%20of%20traditions.%20This%20dual%20approach%20enables%20the%20BJP%20to%20penetrate%20the%20Muslim%20demographic%20while%20retaining%20conservative%20Hindu%20votes.%20Minority%20Muslim%20groups%2C%20in%20turn%2C%20gain%20social%20influence%20and%20benefit%20from%20their%20political%20affiliations%20with%20the%20ruling%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EElectoral%20complexities%3A%20the%20balancing%20act%20of%20political%20interests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20standpoint%2C%20their%20outreach%20to%20the%20Pasmanda%20community%20is%20a%20calculated%20political%20manoeuvre.%20It%20aims%20to%20broaden%20its%20political%20base%20by%20engaging%20a%20substantial%20portion%20of%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%99s%20historically%20underrepresented%20Muslim%20population.%20This%20move%20also%20serves%20to%20counter%20accusations%20of%20majoritarianism%2C%20presenting%20the%20BJP%20as%20a%20more%20inclusive%20political%20force.%20By%20addressing%20the%20socio-economic%20concerns%20of%20many%20Pasmanda%20Muslims%2C%20often%20hailing%20from%20economically%20disadvantaged%20sections%20of%20society%2C%20the%20BJP%20aims%20to%20showcase%20a%20commitment%20to%20inclusive%20development%20and%20social%20justice.%20However%2C%20in%20reality%2C%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20focus%20lies%20in%20bolstering%20its%20political%20base%20ahead%20of%20the%202024%20general%20elections%2C%20a%20time%20when%20its%20Hindu%20nationalist%20identity%20may%20fall%20short.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%20key%20political%20episodes%20at%20the%20periphery%20of%20Pasmanda%20outreach%20warrant%20scrutiny%20%E2%80%95%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20rejection%20of%20the%20Pasmanda%20community%E2%80%99s%20plea%20for%20inclusion%20in%20the%20Scheduled%20Caste%20quota%2C%20an%20unfavourable%20policy%20stance%20for%20the%20community%2C%20and%20the%20delayed%20caste%20census%2C%20despite%20mounting%20pressure%20from%20the%20Opposition.%20Second%2C%20politically%2C%20the%20BJP%20opposes%20a%20caste%20census%2C%20fearing%20it%20might%20challenge%20its%20Hindutva%20campaign%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%202024%20election.%20The%20Opposition%E2%80%99s%20call%20for%20a%20caste%20census%20and%20a%20separate%20quota%20for%20OBC%20women%20within%20the%2033%25%20reservation%20of%20the%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Reservation%20Bill%20recently%20passed%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20makes%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20strategic%20overtures%20to%20Pasmanda%20Muslims%2C%20constituting%20a%20substantial%2080%25%20of%C2%A0%3Cspan%3EIndia%3C%2Fspan%3E%E2%80%98s%20Muslim%20population%2C%20are%20marked%20by%20intricate%20political%20dynamics.%20While%20the%20party%20has%20gained%20support%20from%20minority%20Muslim%20factions%20like%20Sufis%2C%20Shias%2C%20and%20Bohras%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20it%20does%20not%20command%20the%20majority%20of%20Pasmanda%20votes%20independently%2C%20underscoring%20the%20diverse%20political%20allegiances%20within%20this%20community.%20This%20electoral%20complexity%20highlights%20the%20nuanced%20terrain%20the%20BJP%20must%20navigate%20in%20its%20pursuit%20of%20Pasmanda%20support.%20Addi