Delhi%20and%20Ottawa.%20The%20statement%20came%20just%20hours%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcanada-pulls-41-diplomats-from-india-amid-row-what-it-means-4498594%5C%22%3ECanada%20withdrew%2041%20diplomats%3C%2Fa%3E%20accusing%20India%20of%20violating%20the%20Vienna%20Convention%20on%20Diplomatic%20Relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20reject%20any%20attempt%20to%20portray%20the%20implementation%20of%20parity%20as%20a%20violation%20of%20international%20norms%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20external%20affairs%20ministry%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20state%20of%20our%20bilateral%20relations%2C%20the%20much%20higher%20number%20of%20Canadian%20diplomats%20in%20India%2C%20and%20their%20continued%20interference%20in%20our%20internal%20affairs%20warrant%20a%20parity%20in%20mutual%20diplomatic%20presence%20in%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Ottawa%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20today%2C%20Canadian%20Foreign%20Minister%20Melanie%20Joly%20announced%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fcanada-forced-to-repatriate-41-diplomats-from-india-foreign-minister-4498288%5C%22%3E41%20diplomats%20have%20been%20recalled%20from%20India.%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20confirm%20that%20India%20has%20formally%20conveyed%20its%20plan%20to%20unethically%20remove%20diplomatic%20immunities%20for%20all%20but%2021%20Canadian%20diplomats%20and%20dependents%20in%20Delhi%20by%20tomorrow%2C%20October%2020.%20This%20means%2041%20Canadian%20diplomats%20and%20their%2042%20dependents%20were%20in%20danger%20of%20having%20immunity%20stripped%20on%20an%20arbitrary%20date.%20And%20this%20would%20put%20their%20personal%20safety%20at%20risk%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BImmunities%20allow%20diplomats%20to%20do%20their%20work%20without%20fear%20of%20reprisal%20or%20arrests%20from%20the%20country%20they're%20in.%20They%20are%20a%20fundamental%20principle%20of%20diplomacy%20and%20this%20is%20a%20two-way%20street.%20They%20only%20work%20if%20every%20country%20abides%20by%20the%20rules.%20A%20unilateral%20revocation%20of%20diplomatic%20privilege%20and%20immunities%20is%20contrary%20to%20international%20law.%20It%20is%20a%20clear%20violation%20of%20the%20Vienna%20Convention%20on%20Diplomatic%20Relations%20and%20threatening%20to%20do%20so%20is%20unreasonable%20and%20escalatory%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECanada%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-canada-diplomatic-row-justin-trudeau-khalistani-terrorist-canada-urges-citizens-in-india-to-exercise-high-degree-of-caution-as-row-escalates-4498838%5C%22%3Epaused%20all%20in-person%20services%20at%20the%20consulates%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20Chandigarh%2C%20and%20Bengaluru%20and%20urged%20its%20citizens%20in%20these%20three%20cities%20to%20exercise%20caution.%20All%20Canadians%20in%20India%20have%20been%20asked%20to%20contact%20the%20High%20Commission%20in%20New%20Delhi%20in%20case%20they%20need%20assistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20last%20month%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-canada-trade-talk-paused-why-relations-between-the-two-countries-have-soured-4395085%5C%22%3Easked%20Canada%20to%20reduce%20its%20diplomatic%20presence%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20cited%20what%20he%20said%20was%20credible%20evidence%20of%20a%20potential%20link%20between%20Indian%20agents%20and%20the%20murder%20of%20Khalistani%20extremist%20Hardeep%20Singh%20Nijjar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20denies%20any%20connection%20to%20the%20shooting%20outside%20a%20Sikh%20temple%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697799720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2F122o7v0g_modi-trudeau-afp_625x300_23_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparity-in-mutual-diplomatic-presence-india-on-c