y%20have%20been%20the%20first%20female%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fegypt-mummy-burial-ground-of-the-pharaohs-could-change-history-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epharaoh%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20ancient%20Egypt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20they%20are%20right%2C%20the%20discovery%20could%20rewrite%20the%20history%20of%20ancient%20Egypt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E5%2C000-year-old%20wine%20and%20the%20remains%20of%2041%20people%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20excavation%20of%20Meret-Neith's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F3000-year-old-ancient-city-discovered-egypt-lost-golden-city-2021-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrave%3C%2Fa%3E%20revealed%20the%20mud-brick%20tomb%20was%20lined%20with%20large%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fegypt-2600-year-old-pots-cheese-found-at-pharaohs-necropolis-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewine%20jars%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20containing%20dried%20grape%20seeds%2C%20according%20to%20a%20press%20release%20from%20the%20University%20of%20Vienna.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20wine%20jars%20were%20still%20sealed%20with%20the%20stoppers%20intact.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20queen's%20tomb%20was%20also%20surrounded%20by%20the%20graves%20of%2041%20courtiers%20and%20servants.%20Archaeological%20evidence%20suggests%20these%20were%20built%20over%20a%20long%20period%20of%20time%2C%20so%20it's%20likely%20that%20they%20were%20buried%20near%20Meret%20Neiths%20as%20they%20died%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmisconceptions-about-ancient-egyptians-mummies-cleopatra-that-are-wrong-experts-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erather%20than%20being%20killed%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20accompany%20the%20queen%20in%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20most%20certainly%20is%20a%20tremendously%20important%20tomb%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ronald%20Leprohon%2C%20an%20Egyptologist%20and%20emeritus%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Toronto%2C