l%20year%2C%20with%206%2C403%20kilometres%20of%20roads%20constructed%20against%20a%20target%20of%206%2C000%20km%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Frural-road-construction-sees-turnaround-for-the-first-time-in-8-years-nso-123101900924_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBusiness%20Standard%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20cited%20the%20National%20Statistical%20Office%20(NSO)%20in%20its%20latest%20Twenty%20Point%20Programme%20(TPP)%20progress%20report%20for%20the%20April-June%20quarter%20of%20FY24.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20in%20eight%20years%20that%20the%20scheme%20has%20achieved%20its%20first-quarter%20target.%20It%20has%20been%20under-performing%20in%20recent%20years.%20The%20worst%20performance%20was%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%20FY19%20when%20only%209%25%20of%20the%20target%20was%20achieved.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20April-June%202016%2C%20the%20scheme%20only%20achieved%2071%25%20of%20its%20target%2C%20followed%20by%20completion%20of%2075%25%20of%20the%20works%20in%20the%20following%20year%2C%20the%20business%20daily%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20April-September%202022%2C%20only%2041%25%20of%20the%20target%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cmie.com%2Fkommon%2Fbin%2Fsr.php%3Fkall%3Dwarticle%26dt%3D20230130115811%26msec%3D626%5C%22%3Ecould%20be%20constructed%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20the%20stipulated%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Ministry%20of%20Statistics%20and%20Programme%20Implementation%20monitors%20the%20programme%E2%80%99s%20performance%20and%20considers%20it%20%E2%80%9Cpoor%E2%80%9D%20if%20it%20falls%20below%2080%25%20of%20its%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ECurrently%20in%20its%20third%20phase%2C%20PMGSY%20focuses%20on%20consolidating%20the%20rural%20road%20network%20to%20connect%20agricultural%20markets%2C%20schools%2C%20and%20hospitals.%20It%20is%20part%20of%20a%20poverty-reduction%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20budget%20allocation%20for%20the%20programme%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbudget%2Funion-budget-2023-many-surprises-on-rural-development-front-9981821.html%5C%22%3Eremained%20the%20same%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Rs%2019%2C000%20crores%20in%20the%202023-24%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20time%20the%20scheme%20had%20achieved%20its%20target%20was%20in%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%202015.%20It%20had%20surpassed%20its%20target%20by%20206%25%20and%20the%20total%20length%20of%20constructed%20roads%20stood%20at%2010%2C726%20km%20as%20against%20the%20targeted%205%2C200%20km%20in%20the%20quarter%2C%20the%20newspaper%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELaunched%20in%202005%2C%20PMGSY%20was%20a%20centrally%20sponsored%20scheme.%20%3Cspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-IN%5C%22%3EFrom%202015-16%2C%20the%20funding%20is%20being%20shared%20between%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20states%20in%20the%20ratio%20of%2060%3A40.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frwdbihar.gov.in%2FSchemePMGSY.aspx%5C%22%3Egovernment%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20primary%20objective%20of%20the%20PMGSY%20is%20to%20provide%20connectivity%2C%20by%20way%20of%20an%20all-weather%20road%20(with%20necessary%20culverts%20and%20cross-drainage%20structures%2C%20which%20is%20operable%20throughout%20the%20year)%2C%20to%20the%20not%20connected%20habitations%20so%20far%20in%20the%20rural%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20written%20response%20submitted%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Union%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20rural%20development%2C%20Sadhvi%20Niranjan%20Jyoti%2C%20said%20that%20only%2018%2C983%20km%20out%20of%20the%20sanctioned%2099%2C319%20km%20have%20been%20completed%20in%20the%20third%20phase%2C%20covering%20the%20period%20from%20FY20%20to%20FY25.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20phase%20focuses%20on%20consolidating%20of%20the%20rural%20road%20network%20c