endence%20to%20power%20in%20the%20combined%20state%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20in%202004.%20Barring%20stray%20protests%20to%20highlight%20unemployment%20and%20failures%20of%20the%20government%2C%20the%20Congress%20never%20really%20took%20on%20the%20ruling%20regime%20in%20Telangana.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20what%20is%20it%20that%20puts%20the%20Congress%20on%20an%20even%20keel%20or%20even%20stronger%20than%20the%20BRS%20in%20the%20upcoming%20contest%3F%20It%20is%20all%20because%20of%20the%20failures%20of%20the%20BRS%20government%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20gained.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%20elections%2C%20it%20is%20visible%20that%20people%20are%20turning%20against%20the%20BRS.%20But%20strangely%2C%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20which%20was%20expected%20to%20be%20another%20alternative%2C%20failed%20to%20make%20headway%2C%20though%20it%20tried%20to%20whip%20up%20its%20strategy%20of%20religious%20polarisation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20helped%20Congress%20in%20this%20scenario%20were%20the%20frequent%20attacks%20on%20the%20BRS%20launched%20by%20the%20former%20party%E2%80%99s%20state%20unit%20president%2C%20A.%20Revanth%20Reddy.%20His%20BJP%20counterpart%2C%20Bandi%20Sanjay%20Kumar%2C%20was%20also%20equally%20aggressive%20against%20the%20BRS%20and%20chief%20minister%20K.%20Chandrashekar%20Rao%20(KCR)%2C%20until%20he%20was%20eased%20out%20of%20the%20post%20earlier%20this%20year%20to%20pave%20way%20for%20Union%20minister%20G.%20Kishan%20Reddy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftelangana-polls-brs-kcr-congress-bjp%5C%22%3ETelangana%20Polls%3A%20BRS%20Has%20Reason%20Not%20to%20Be%20Overconfident%20With%20Congress%20Poised%20to%20Challenge%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETelangana%20was%20a%20hotbed%20of%20resentment%20among%20the%20youngsters%20over%20unemployment%20in%20the%20last%20few%20months%2C%20following%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fhyderabad%2Ftelangana-public-service-commission-paper-leak-staffers-police-constable-among-9-arrested-8495636%2F%5C%22%3Eleakage%20of%20question%20papers%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20half-a-dozen%20recruitment%20exams%20conducted%20by%20the%20State%20Public%20Service%20Commission.%20The%20protests%20by%20youngsters%20were%20put%20down%20with%20an%20iron%20hand%20by%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20issue%2C%20coupled%20with%20the%20prevailing%20anti-incumbency%20sentiment%2C%20which%20was%20fuelled%20by%20the%20feeling%20that%20KCR%E2%80%99s%20family%20amassed%20wealth%20and%20that%20populist%20policies%20for%20various%20sections%20of%20society%20were%20mere%20eyewash%20to%20cover%20up%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20failures.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20anti-incumbency%20sentiment%20is%20gaining%20further%20ground%20because%20of%20an%20emotive%20issue%3A%20the%20feeling%20that%20the%20real%20estate%20businesses%20and%20other%20enterprises%20owned%20by%20people%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20origin%20are%20continuing.%20This%2C%20people%20feel%2C%20runs%20contrary%20to%20the%20main%20plank%20of%20the%20Telangana%20statehood%20movement%2C%20that%20the%20region%20was%20exploited%20by%20politicians%20and%20businessmen%20from%20Andhra.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20context%2C%20the%20Bharat%20Jodo%20yatra%2C%20launched%20by%20Congress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20was%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20for%20the%20party.%20The%20yatra%20and%20Reddy%E2%80%99s%20outbursts%20against%20KCR%20infused%20a%20refreshing%20confidence%20in%20the%20party%20cadre.%20The%20party%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fhyderabad%2Fcongress-will-give-2-lakh-jobs-within-a-year-if-voted-to-power-in-telangana-says-revanth-reddy%2Farticleshow%2F99794861.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ehas%20also%20promised%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20create%20two%20lakh%20jobs%20within%20a%20year%20of%20coming%20to%20power%20and%20a%20calendar%20to%20fill%20up%20rising%20governemnt%20vacancies%20on%20a%20monthly%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20Working%20Committee%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Forganisational-unity-of-utmost-importance-says-kharge-as-congress-chalks-out-poll-strategy%5C%22%3Emeeting%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Hyderabad%20and%20a%20massive%20public%20meeting%20addressed%20by%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20on%20the%20outskirts%20on%20September%2016%20and%2017%20gave%20further%20impetus%20to%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20growing%20popularity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20uptick%20in%20the%20fortunes%20of%20the%20party%20ahead%20of%20the%20electoral%20battle%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fbrs-bjp-netas-to-join-congress-in-rahul-gandhis-presence%2Farticleshow%2F104510134.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Eis%20reflected%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20interest%20to%20join%20the%20party%20by%20a%20number%20of%20leaders%20from%20the%20BRS%20and%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20past%20two%20elections%2C%20the%20Congress%20lost%20a%20big%20chunk%20of%20its%20MLAs%20to%20the%20BRS%20(then%20TRS).%20In%202014%2C%2010%20of%20its%2021%20MLAs%20defected%20while%20in%202018%2C%2013%20of%2019%20did.%20With%20several%20disgruntled%20leaders%20flocking%20to%20it%20before%20the%20election%2C%20Congress%20appears%20to%20be%20in%20an%20upbeat%20mood.%20This%20could%20be%20seen%20from%20the%20hectic%20activity%20at%20Gandhi%20Bhavan%2C%20the%20party%20headquarters%2C%20with%20the%20campus%20and%20corridors%20full%20of%20leaders%20and%20supporters%20wanting%20tickets%20to%20contest%20polls.%20Protests%20have%20also%20erupted%20due%20to%20denial%20of%20tickets%2C%20with%20the%20finalisation%20of%20candidates%20for%20more%20than%20half%20of%20the%20total%20seats%20still%20pending.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1697794210000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20134258%2FF80iGYpasAEo0kc.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpo