%20not%20said%20anything%20on%20the%20issue%20officially%2C%20but%20it%20appears%20he%20is%20facing%20eight%20charges%2C%20including%20disobeying%20a%20superior%20officer%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2023%2F10%2F20%2Fpolitics%2Ftravis-king-desertion%2Findex.html%5C%22%3Ereported%C2%A0%3Cem%3ECNN%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%2023-year-old%20was%20detained%20on%20Wednesday%20at%20Fort%20Bliss%2C%20Texas%2C%20the%20outlet%20further%20said%20citing%20a%20source%20familiar%20to%20the%20matter%2C%20who%20said%20he%20is%20being%20held%20in%20pre-trial%20detention.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrivate%20King's%20mother%20Claudine%20Gates%20issued%20a%20statement%20in%20which%20she%20said%20she%20loves%20her%20son%20%26quot%3Bunconditionally%26quot%3B%20and%20is%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20concerned%20about%20his%20mental%20health.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20his%20mother%2C%20I%20ask%20that%20my%20son%20be%20afforded%20the%20presumption%20of%20innocence%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Gates%20told%20%3Cem%3ECNN%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20mother%20knows%20her%20son%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20something%20happened%20to%20mine%20while%20he%20was%20deployed.%20The%20Army%20promised%20to%20investigate%20what%20happened%20at%20Camp%20Humphries%2C%20and%20I%20await%20the%20results%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrivate%20King%20was%20on%20duty%20with%20the%20US%20Army%20when%20he%20crossed%20the%20North%20Korean%20border.%20He%20had%20been%20in%20the%20Army%20since%20January%202021%20and%20was%20based%20in%20South%20Korea%20as%20part%20of%20a%20rotation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20border%20crossing%20came%20with%20relations%20between%20the%20two%20Koreas%20at%20one%20of%20their%20lowest%20points%20ever%2C%20with%20diplomacy%20stalled%20and%20North%20Korean%20leader%20Kim%20Jong%20Un%20calling%20for%20increased%20weapons%20development%2C%20including%20tactical%20nuclear%20warheads.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAround%20half%20a%2