%20by%20suicide%3C%2Fa%3E%20demanding%20reservations%20for%20the%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESunil%20Kavle%2C%20a%20Maratha%20activist%20from%20Jalna%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fmaharashtra-quota-suicide-poses-new-challenge-for-eknath-shinde-govt%2Farticleshow%2F104563975.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Eleft%20a%20three-page%20suicide%20note%3C%2Fa%3E%20stating%20that%20he%20was%20ending%20his%20life%20seeking%20reservations%20for%20his%20community%20before%20hanging%20himself%20from%20a%20a%20flyover%20in%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20death%20comes%20just%20five%20days%20before%20the%20deadline%20set%20by%20Maratha%20leader%20Manoj%20Jarange%20Patil%20who%20has%20threatened%20a%20wider%20agitation%20if%20the%20Marathas%20were%20not%20recognised%20as%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20(OBCs)%20by%20October%2024%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fmaharashtra-quota-suicide-poses-new-challenge-for-eknath-shinde-govt%2Farticleshow%2F104563975.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKavle%E2%80%99s%20family%20said%20that%20the%20government%20should%20honour%20his%20last%20wishes%20and%20provide%20reservations%20to%20the%20Marathas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20(state)%20government%20is%20responsible%20for%20this.%20There%20is%20a%20view%20within%20the%20community%20that%20the%20government%20is%20deliberately%20not%20giving%20Marathas%20reservations.%20The%20government%20should%20not%20keep%20the%20Marathas%20waiting%20but%20ensure%20that%20they%20are%20given%20reservations%20soon.%20I%20am%20imploring%20the%20Maratha%20youth%20to%20not%20take%20any%20drastic%20steps.%20We%20will%20have%20a%20peaceful%20stir%20but%20we%20will%20get%20reservation%20for%20our%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20Patil%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fmaharashtra-quota-suicide-poses-new-challenge-for-eknath-shinde-govt%2Farticleshow%2F104563975.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20another%20Maratha%20youth%20ended%20his%20life%20seeking%20quota%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fexplainer-why-the-maratha-quota-agitation-has-put-successive-maharashtra-governments-in-a-bind%5C%22%3EExplainer%3A%20Why%20the%20Maratha%20Quota%20Agitation%20Has%20Put%20Successive%20Maharashtra%20Governments%20in%20a%20Bind%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENationalist%20Congress%20Party%20MP%20Supriya%20Sule%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fmaharashtra-quota-suicide-poses-new-challenge-for-eknath-shinde-govt%2Farticleshow%2F104563975.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20a%20totally%20insensitive%20government.%20Under%20this%20triple%20engine%20government%2C%20they%20have%20not%20been%20able%20to%20give%20reservation%20to%20the%20Dhangar%20(shepherd)%20community%2C%20Muslims%2C%20Lingayats%20and%20Marathas.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Maratha%20quota%20protests%20had%20begun%20on%20August%2029%20when%20Patil%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fexplainer-why-the-maratha-quota-agitation-has-put-successive-maharashtra-governments-in-a-bind%5C%22%3Ea%20Maratha%20activist%20from%20Jalna%2C%20sat%20on%20an%20indefinite%20hunger%20strike%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20reviving%20a%20three-decade%20old%20demand%20for%20Maratha%20reservations.%20In%20some%20places%2C%20the%20agitation%20turned%20violent%20with%20the%20police%20resorting%20to%20lathi-charge%20on%20the%20protesters%2C%20further%20worsening%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Maharashtra%20government%20apologised%20for%20the%20lathi-charge%20and%20later%20announced%20that%20Kunbi%2