e%20and%20Israel%2C%20arguing%20that%20this%20was%20an%20investment%20for%20the%20United%20States'%20future%20as%20a%20global%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20smart%20investment%20that's%20going%20to%20pay%20dividends%20for%20American%20security%20for%20generations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%2080-year-old%20Democrat%20said%20in%20just%20the%20second%20speech%20of%20his%20presidency%20delivered%20from%20behind%20the%20historic%20Resolute%20Desk.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmerican%20leadership%20is%20what%20holds%20the%20world%20together.%20American%20alliances%20are%20what%20keep%20us%2C%20America%2C%20safe.%20American%20values%20are%20what%20make%20us%20a%20partner%20that%20other%20nations%20want%20to%20work%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAmerica%20is%20a%20beacon%20to%20the%20world.%20Still.%20Still%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFresh%20from%20a%20whirlwind%20trip%20to%20Israel%20this%20week%2C%20Biden%20wants%20to%20win%20over%20war-weary%20voters%20and%20hardline%20Republicans%20as%20he%20ramps%20up%20his%202024%20reelection%20bid.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20is%20said%20to%20be%20teeing%20up%20a%20huge%20request%20to%20Congress%20for%20a%20%24100%20billion%20package%20that%20would%20include%20funding%20for%20Israel%20in%20its%20war%20with%20Hamas%20and%20also%20for%20Ukraine's%20battle%20against%20Russian%20invasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETying%20together%20two%20conflicts%20an%20ocean%20away%20from%20the%20United%20States%20is%20a%20bid%20by%20Biden%20to%20frame%20them%20as%20part%20of%20a%20bigger%20struggle%20to%20shape%20the%20world%20order%20and%20protect%20Americans%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E-%20Somber%20setting%20of%20Oval%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPresidents%20traditionally%20reserve%20speeches%20from%20the%20solemn%20setting%20of%20the%20Oval%20Office%20for%20moments%20of%20key%20national%20significance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBiden's%20only%20previous%20address%20from%20there%20was%20in%20June%20when%20he%20hailed%20a%20deal%20with%20Congress%20to%20avert%20what%20would%20have%20been%20a%20catastrophic%20US%20debt%20default.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20Congress%20has%20now%20been%20paralyzed%20for%20more%20than%20two%20weeks%20as%20divided%20Republicans%2C%20who%20control%20the%20majority%20in%20the%20House%2C%20fail%20repeatedly%20to%20agree%20on%20electing%20a%20House%20speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHard-right%20Republicans%2C%20and%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20voters%2C%20are%20also%20strongly%20opposed%20to%20adding%20to%20the%20%2443.9%20billion%20in%20security%20assistance%20that%20the%20United%20States%20has%20committed%20to%20Ukraine%20since%20Moscow%20launched%20its%20full-scale%20invasion%20in%20February%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUS%20media%20reported%20that%20Friday's%20package%20request%20will%20include%20%2410%20billion%20in%20emergency%20assistance%20for%20Israel%20and%20%2460%20billion%20for%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJust%20before%20the%20speech%2C%20Biden%20spoke%20to%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EZelensky%20welcomed%20the%20recent%20delivery%20of%20ATACMS%20long-range%20missiles%20from%20the%20United%20States%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BUkraine%20is%20grateful%20for%20the%20vital%20and%20enduring%20US%20support%20in%20our%20fight%20for%20freedom%20and%20against%20Russian%20aggression.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBiden%20has%20also%20been%20striking%20a%20statesmanlike%20tone%20on%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war%20with%20an%20eye%20on%20US%20voters%20where%20there%20is%20strong%20support%20for%20Israel%20--%20even%20if%20leftwing%20Democrats%20oppose%20his%20stance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20Tel%20Aviv%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20Biden%20backed%20Israel%20as%20it%20gears%20up%20for%20a%20ground%20invasion%20of%20Gaza%20after%20the%20October%207%20attacks%20by%20the%20Palestinian%20militant%20group%20Hamas%20which%20killed%20more%20than%201%2C400%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20also%20brokered%20a