%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-67166644.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-africa-67166644.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20I%20Can%E2%80%99t%20Find%20a%20Good%20Plumber%3A%20Exploring%20the%20%E2%80%98Skill%20India'%20Mess%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F19165415%2Fimage-1409.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20Rati%20Bhan%20ji%E2%80%99s%20number%20on%20the%20speed%20dial%2C%20but%20reaching%20him%20is%20not%20so%20easy.%20He%20is%20one%20of%20the%20busiest%20men%20in%20north%20Delhi.%20He%20arrived%20with%20an%20apprentice%20and%20got%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20why%20I%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20able%20to%20access%20water%20in%20my%20newly%20rented%20flat.%20Fighting%20through%20pigeons%20and%20a%20mini%20jungle%20with%20reptilian%20infestation%20on%20the%20terrace%2C%20he%20reached%20the%20overhead%20tank%20%E2%80%93%20which%20leaked.%20The%20solution%3A%20fit%20a%20new%20tank%2C%20a%20whole%20day%E2%80%99s%20job%2C%20after%20negotiating%20with%20the%20landlord.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EI%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20so%20lucky%20when%20I%20needed%20him%20for%20the%20second%20time.%20He%20was%20engaged%20with%20L%26amp%3BT%20on%20a%20contractual%20basis%20for%20an%20upcoming%20block%20of%20residential%20apartments%20in%20Noida.%20I%20was%20impressed%2C%20because%20a%20plumber%20who%20is%20no%20longer%20young%20but%20good%20at%20his%20work%20was%20in%20demand%20all%20over%20Delhi-NCR.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20made%20me%20realise%20why%20some%20aggregators%20have%20cashed%20in%20on%20the%20shortage%20of%20plumbers%2C%20electricians%2C%20carpenters%2C%20and%20masons%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20supposed%20to%20get%20over%20this%20shortage%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20disdain%20for%20working%20class%20people%2C%20with%20Skill%20India%2C%20a%20flagship%20scheme%20that%20was%20launched%20in%202015.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20a%20dismal%20placement%20record%20and%20absurdly%20short%20training%20programmes%2C%20where%20overzealous%20private%20players%20have%20replicated%20the%20public%20infrastructure%20of%20Industrial%20Training%20Institutes%2C%20instead%20of%20building%20upon%20it.%20This%20has%20happened%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20government%20think%20tank%20NITI%20Aayog%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fjobs%2Ffresher%2Fenabling-platforms-for-gig-workers-and-their-future%2Farticleshow%2F99081366.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3Ehad%20suggested%3C%2Fa%3E%20ways%20to%20resuscitate%20it%2C%20as%20recently%20as%20January%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Skill%20India%20and%20PMKVY%20are%20inadequate%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20Rati%20Bhan%20ji%20again%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20for%20a%20plumbing%20consultation.%20I%20wanted%20to%20discuss%20with%20him%20India%E2%80%99s%20skill%20programmes.%20I%20wanted%20to%20understand%C2%A0why%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%20find%20a%20good%20plumber%20when%20Rati%20Bhan%20ji%20is%20busy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20114909%2Fimage0.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20114909%2Fimage0.jpeg%20900w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20114909%2Fimage0-225x300.jpeg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F20114909%2Fimage0-768x1024.jpeg%20768w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-680962%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ERati%20Bhan%20ji%2C%20a%20plumber%20since%201996%2C%20says%20to%20be%20able%20to%20work%20on%20site%2C%20independently%2C%20a%20plumber%20needs%20five%20years%20of%20training%20mixed%20with%20experience.%20Photo%20provided%20by%20author.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20returned%20from%20Singapore%2C%20triggering%20class%20arrogance%20in%20me.%20He%20was%20on%20training%2C%20funded%20by%20a%20pipe%20company%20that%20wanted%20to%20put%20him%20in%20charge%20of%20a%20project%20in%20Mumbai.%20The%20training%20was%20not%20part%20of%20the%20Skill%20India%20mission%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pmkvyofficial.org%2F%5C%22%3EPradhan%20Mantri%20Kaushal%20Vikas%20Yojana%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20was%20not%20a%20wasteful%20two-month%20course%20for%20newbies%2C%20ill-suited%20to%20take%20the%20rough%20and%20tumble%20of%20plumbing%2C%20who%20will%20drop%20out%20of%20the%20trade%20in%20no%20time.%20Out%20of%20ten%20plumbers%2C%20less%20than%20two%20trained%20by%20Skill%20India%20stick%20around%2C%20practitioners%20who%20source%20from%20the%20mission%20told%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Singapore%20stint%20was%20training%20in%20best%20practices%20for%20Rati%20Bhan%20ji%2C%20who%20has%20been%20a%20plumber%20since%201996.%20He%20works%20on%20site%20with%20a%20team%20of%20senior%20and%20junior%20masons%2C%20and%20helpers%2C%20and%20labour.%20He%20is%20so%20experienced%20that%20he%20can%20detect%2C%20even%20from%20a%20description%20over%20the%20phone%2C%20where%20his%20team%20is%20getting%20stuck.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20kind%20of%20training%20is%20not%20provided%20in%20the%20Skill%20India%20syllabi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Plumbing%20Association%20told%20me%20the%20correct%20way%20of%20training%20new%20plumbers%3A%20it%20should%20be%20a%20modular%20course%20consisting%20of%20at%20least%20eight%20modules%2C%20stretching%20over%2015%20days%20each.%20The%20modules%20should%20not%20be%20taught%20in%20continuity%20because%20plumbers%2C%20after%20all%2C%20have%20to%20earn%20between%20their%20training.%20The%20spaced-modules%20programme%20also%20lets%20the%20job%20market%20test%20out%20a%20plumber%E2%80%99s%20stickability.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERati%20Bhan%20ji%20feels%20that%20while%20he%20can%20train%20an%20apprentice%20in%20a%20month%20to%20do%20plumbing%20of%20a%20basic%20bathroom%2C%20anything%20more%20will%20need%20a%20year.%20And%20to%20emerge%20as%20a%20plumber%20who%20can%20do%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ebade%20se%20bada%20kaam%20and%20chote%20se%20chota%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0or%20in%20other%20words%2C%20work%20on%20a%20site%2C%20will%20take%20five%20years%20of%20training%20mixed%20with%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20sticking%20around%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20against%20this%2C%20Skill%20India%20tries%20to%20prepare%20a%20plumber%20in%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERohit%20Jadhav%2C%20who%20runs%20Swastik%20Plumbing%20and%20Home%20Services%20in%20Pune%2C%20said%20plumbing%20is%20a%20rough%20trade%20and%20new%20recruits%20simply%20give%20up%20and%20leave.%20Both%20Jadhav%20and%20Rati%20Bhan%20ji%20estimate%20that%20less%20than%2020%25%20of%20those%20entering%20the%20plumbing%20trade%20stick%20with%20it%20for%20the%20long%20term.%20India%E2%80%99s%20high%20and%20mounting%20heatwaves%20make%20it%20extremely%20difficult%20for%20a%20trade%20to%20be%20practised%20largely%20in%20the%20open.%20In%20addition%2C%20the%20Indian%20companies%E2%80%99%20reluctance%20to%20provide%20basic%20equipment%20such%20as%20helmets%20and%20shoes%20to%20plumbers%20make%20it%20even%20more%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20heat%2C%20a%20bathroom%20can%20become%20a%20furnace.%20This%20generation%20also%20wants%20to%20step%20out%20in%20ironed%20clothes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rati%20Bhan%20ji%20said%2C%20counting%20the%20various%20factors.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20those%20who%20manage%20to%20adjust%20to%20the%20job%2C%20and%20prove%20themselves%20to%20be%20good%20at%20it%2C%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJayashree%20Narode%2C%20a%20plumber%2C%20was%20featured%20on%20the%20Facebook%20page%20of%20Pratham%20Livelihoods%2C%20Skilling%2