ches%20across%20Mumbai%20and%20Hyderabad%2C%20with%20plans%20of%20opening%20three%20more%20in%20Hyderabad%20this%20month.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20saw%20everyone%20moving%20to%20healthier%20consumption%20and%20one%20of%20the%20food%20items%20prescribed%20by%20doctors%20is%20always%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20be%20it%20the%20dal%20khichdi%20in%20the%20north%20to%20your%20%3Cem%3Epongal%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20the%20south.%20This%20saw%20a%20boom%20for%20businesses%20like%20Khichdi%20Express%2C%20as%20more%20people%20started%20ordering%20the%20dish.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20orders%20from%20hospitals%2C%20isolation%20centres%20and%20people%20at%20home.%20We%20distributed%20free%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20people%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20Mumbai.%20People%20would%20call%20us%20with%20instructions%20asking%20for%20less%20spices.%20They%20would%20call%20us%20after%20their%20family%20members%20recovered%20and%20thank%20us.%20It%20was%20a%20rewarding%20moment.%20We%20felt%20great%20as%20our%20food%20could%20heal%20people%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELavanya%2C%20a%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E%20lover%20who%20stays%20in%20Banjara%20Hills%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20says%20that%20she%E2%80%99s%20been%20ordering%20from%20Khichdi%20Express%20for%20the%20past%20one%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTheir%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdis%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20very%20tasty%20and%20fill%20your%20stomach.%20Their%20regular%20dal%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20very%20sumptuous%20and%20is%20my%20favourite.%20I%20found%20them%20through%20the%20food-delivery%20app%2C%20Zomato.%20For%20daily%20meals%20for%20office-goers%20like%20me%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20blessing%20and%20a%20complete%20meal%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Lavanya.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAbha%20says%20that%20people%20laughed%20at%20her%20when%20she%20spoke%20about%20starting%20a%20%3Cem%3Ekhichdi%3C%2Fem%3E%20business.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20told%20me%20that%20%3